<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 00:59:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国习近平在区域会议前支持斐济总理的太平洋计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-backs-fijian-pms-pacific-plan-ahead-regional-meeting-2024-08-21/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国国家主席习近平周二在北京举行的一次会议上对来访的斐济总理西蒂维尼·拉布卡表示，他支持他的“和平海洋”计划，几天后，太平洋岛国领导人将在汤加举行峰会。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 00:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-backs-fijian-pms-pacific-plan-ahead-regional-meeting-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，沃尔玛寻求通过出售京东股份筹集至多 37.4 亿美元的资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/walmart-seeks-raise-374-bln-sale-jdcom-stake-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-08-20/</link><description>彭博社周二援引知情人士的话报道称，美国零售商沃尔玛正寻求通过出售其在中国电子商务公司京东的股份筹集至多 37.4 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 23:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/walmart-seeks-raise-374-bln-sale-jdcom-stake-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：随着市场整合，两次利率电话即将召开</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-20/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 21:52:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>美国称秘密核战略不是针对单一国家或威胁的回应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-approved-secret-nuclear-strategy-focusing-chinese-threat-new-york-times-2024-08-20/</link><description>在《纽约时报》报道称白宫调整了美国威慑战略以重点关注中国扩张核武力量后，白宫周二表示，乔·拜登总统今年批准的机密核战略计划不是针对单一国家或威胁的回应。阿森纳第一次。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 19:53:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-approved-secret-nuclear-strategy-focusing-chinese-threat-new-york-times-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>美国在华临床试验遭美国议员质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-clinical-trials-china-questioned-by-us-lawmakers-2024-08-20/</link><description>周二，一个两党议员小组呼吁拜登政府加强对在中国进行的美国临床试验的审查，理由是知识产权被盗的风险以及维吾尔人被迫参与的可能性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 17:07:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-clinical-trials-china-questioned-by-us-lawmakers-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国Antfin持有印度Zomato近一半股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-antfin-nearly-halves-stake-indias-zomato-2024-08-20/</link><description>交易所数据显示，阿里巴巴集团旗下 Antfin 新加坡公司周二出售了印度 Zomato 价值 477.2 亿卢比（合 5.7 亿美元）的股份，将其在这家食品和杂货配送平台的持股比例减少了近一半，至 2.2%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-antfin-nearly-halves-stake-indias-zomato-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>宝马中国产电动Mini将享受21.3%的低关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmws-china-made-electric-mini-receive-lower-213-tariff-2024-08-20/</link><description>宝马表示，其在中国生产电动Mini的合资企业在欧盟最新的中国制造电动汽车关税文件草案中被列为“合作公司”，有资格享受21.3%的较低关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmws-china-made-electric-mini-receive-lower-213-tariff-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，香港SVI关闭了专注于中国的对冲基金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kongs-svi-winds-down-china-focused-hedge-fund-say-sources-2024-08-20/</link><description>三名消息人士称，总部位于香港的对冲基金战略愿景投资（SVI）已缩减其投资于中国股票的主要价值乘数基金。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 12:26:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kongs-svi-winds-down-china-focused-hedge-fund-say-sources-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称被指控与中国犯罪有关的前市长已逃离该国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-ex-mayor-accused-chinese-crime-links-has-fled-country-2024-08-20/</link><description>菲律宾一个城镇的一名前市长因涉嫌与中国犯罪集团有联系而接受调查，她已逃离该国，促使菲律宾总统办公室周一下令吊销她的护照。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:51:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-ex-mayor-accused-chinese-crime-links-has-fled-country-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中信、中金等10家券商被纳入中国大湾区财富计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/citic-cicc-among-10-brokerages-included-chinas-greater-bay-area-wealth-scheme-2024-08-20/</link><description>两位知情人士告诉路透社，中国和香港将扩大试点财富计划，允许居民进行跨境投资，首批 10 家证券公司将加入其中，其中包括中国最大的券商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:29:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/citic-cicc-among-10-brokerages-included-chinas-greater-bay-area-wealth-scheme-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>由于竞争激烈，小鹏汽车预计季度收入低于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-projects-lower-than-expected-quarterly-revenue-stiff-competition-2024-08-20/</link><description>中国公司小鹏汽车周二预测第三季度收入低于分析师预期，并未达到周二六月季度销售预期，原因是激烈的竞争以及对其老化的昂贵电动汽车产品线的需求下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:44:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-projects-lower-than-expected-quarterly-revenue-stiff-competition-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉将降低其中国制造电动汽车的欧盟关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-slashes-planned-tariff-teslas-china-made-evs-9-2024-08-20/</link><description>欧盟高管周二表示，在特斯拉要求进行进一步调查后，欧盟已将计划对从中国进口的特斯拉电动汽车征收的额外关税削减一半以上。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-slashes-planned-tariff-teslas-china-made-evs-9-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>标准普尔 500 指数狩猎云九</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-20/</link><description>欧洲、中东和非洲地区财经和市场突发新闻记者 Alun John 对美国和全球市场的未来展望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:03:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，根据计划的欧盟关税，大众汽车将获得较低的 Cupra Tavascan 税率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-receive-lower-rate-cupra-tavascan-under-planned-eu-tariffs-source-says-2024-08-20/</link><description>一位知情人士周二表示，根据欧盟委员会对中国制造汽车征收的关税计划，大众汽车在中国的西雅特子公司生产的 Cupra Tavascan 将获得 21.3% 的较低关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 09:41:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-receive-lower-rate-cupra-tavascan-under-planned-eu-tariffs-source-says-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国计划“做大做强”社会保障基金以援助老龄化社会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-bigger-stronger-social-security-fund-aid-ageing-society-2024-08-20/</link><description>中国将加强2.88万亿元人民币（4060亿美元）的社会保障基金，使其“更大更强”，以帮助支持其迅速老龄化的人口，因为新生儿和年轻劳动力的数量正在减少，以供养老年人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 04:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-bigger-stronger-social-security-fund-aid-ageing-society-2024-08-20/</guid></item></channel></rss>